Patient age

sex

Patient sex

Examples

data(survivalcont_test)
if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
survivalcont(
  data = survivalcont_test,
  elapsedtime = "time_months",
  outcome = "outcome",
  outcomeLevel = "Dead",
  contexpl = "biomarker",
  findcut = TRUE,
  sc = TRUE
)
